---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Find a Heat & Glo Dealer Near You | Heat & Glo"
  description="Find a Heat & Glo authorized dealer near you. 1,400+ dealers across the US and Canada. Schedule an in-home consultation, browse fireplaces in person, get installation quotes."
  noIndex={true}
>
  <section class="relative mb-12 -mx-4 overflow-hidden">
    <img src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/c220ce20-e963-4c07-85ca-83fa16359ef4/Nest-Out-West-Basem?io=transform:fill,width:1920,height:720" alt="Renovated basement living space featuring Heat & Glo fireplace as the focal point" class="w-full h-[520px] md:h-[360px] object-cover" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/85 via-black/65 to-black/30 flex items-end pb-10 md:items-center md:pb-0 px-6 md:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-page mx-auto text-white">
        <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-sm font-semibold drop-shadow">Find a Dealer</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 max-w-2xl drop-shadow-lg">An authorized dealer near you.</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <main class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 py-4">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 max-w-2xl">
        Heat & Glo sells through a network of <strong>1,400+ authorized dealers</strong> across the US and Canada. Your local dealer can walk you through the lineup in person, schedule an in-home consultation, and quote installation for your specific space.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- DEMO EXPERIENCE FRAMING PILL -->
    <div class="demo-context-pill" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fef3d8 0%, #fefaf0 100%); border: 1px solid #e8d29b; border-left: 4px solid #c44a08; border-radius: 10px; padding: 18px 22px; margin-bottom: 28px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;">
      <span style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;">🔥</span>
      <div>
        <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #c44a08; margin: 0 0 4px;">Live Pattern Demo · Dealer Locator</p>
        <p style="font-family: 'Roboto', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.55; margin: 0;">Search any ZIP and you'll land on a sample dealer results template. In production, this connects to Heat &amp; Glo's live database of 1,400+ authorized retailers and renders an interactive map. The pattern scales — the data layer wires in last.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="bg-neutral-100 border-2 border-neutral-300 rounded-lg p-8 mb-16">
      <form action="/where-to-buy/results/" method="GET" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <label for="zip" class="sr-only">ZIP or postal code</label>
        <input
          id="zip"
          type="text"
          name="zip"
          placeholder="ZIP or postal code (e.g., 90210)"
          class="flex-1 px-4 py-4 border-2 border-neutral-400 rounded-lg text-base"
          style="background: #fff; color: #1a1a1a;"
        />
        <button type="submit" style="background: #c44a08; color: #fff; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; border: none; transition: background 0.15s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#a83e07'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#c44a08'">
          Find Dealers →
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mt-4">
        Or call <a href="tel:8884273973" class="underline font-medium">888-427-3973</a> to be routed to your nearest dealer directly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-orange-400 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">📅</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Schedule a consultation</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Most dealers offer free in-home consultations to size the right fireplace for your space, walk through fuel options, and quote installation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-orange-400 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">🔥</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">See it installed</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Many dealers maintain showrooms with operating Heat & Glo units across the lineup, so you can compare flame quality, glass treatment, and proportions in person before specifying.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-orange-400 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">🛠️</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Service + parts</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">Your authorized dealer is also your annual service partner. They handle warranty work, parts replacement, and the recommended yearly inspection that keeps your fireplace running long-term.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-lg p-8 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Save up to $650 on a gas insert.</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4 max-w-2xl">Upgrade your old wood-burning fireplace to a Heat & Glo gas insert through your authorized dealer. Push-button warmth, cleaner glass, faster install. Limited-time rebate.</p>
      <a href="/fireplace-sale/" style="background: #c44a08; color: #fff; display: inline-block; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#a83e07'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#c44a08'">See rebate terms →</a>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t pt-10 text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <p>
        Outside the US or Canada? Contact <a href="/get-in-touch/" class="underline">Heat &amp; Glo directly</a> for international dealer inquiries.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
